Goals from Bolton Omwenga and Collins Wendo on Monday helped Kenya Commercial Bank (KCB) FC register a 2-0 victory over Mt. Kenya United in a SportPesa Premier League match at Kenyatta Stadium, Machakos. Omwenga opened the scoring after 18 minutes and Wendo added the second in 48th minute as KCB climbed the log to ninth with 15 points. More to follow...   Soldiers lost 3-1 to Kariobangi Sharks in their last outing.